snippet.title: Marilyn Manson Hit With 3rd Lawsuit, Sued for Alleged Assault and Rape by Ex
snippet.description:
Previously, it was revealed that Marilyn Manson was being sued by ‘Game of Thrones’ actress Esmé Blanco, who claims she was raped and sexually assaulted by the artist. Along with that, the artist was hit with another lawsuit that accused him of similar acts. Now, a third lawsuit was filed against Manson by “Jane Doe,” who says she dated the rock star in 2011.

The person alleges that while they were dating, Manson showed her a video depicting “abuse of a groupie after a 1996 concert” in Hollywood. The person in the video was allegedly threatened with a gun and “forced to drink urine.”

Sources that talked to TMZ claim the video wasn’t real but was supposed to be a short film. However, that film was never made public. In her lawsuit, the accuser also said the movie was locked away in a safe. Jane Doe claims the movie made her “afraid for her life” and that Manson allegedly raped her and threatened her life after she returned to his house to give him back a key.

Manson has yet to address the new allegations against him, with the last time the artist posted on social media being in February 2021.

source: Deadline
